PRIVATE CLIENTSAsset managementTECHNOLOGY & BANKING SERVICES



Private Clients

                    Each relationship starts with a conversation




	Every client’s story is different. Each one is unique.

	We invest significant time to understand your very personal circumstances. We do this for all our clients, who come from increasingly diverse backgrounds: entrepreneurs; corporate executives; family businesses spanning several generations; and younger generations adjusting to newly received family assets.

	The service we offer is bespoke, not one-size-fits-all. And it starts with a question.

	What do you want to achieve with your wealth?

	We believe in a long-term, holistic approach to wealth management that takes into account your investment horizon, risk tolerance, family situation and how actively you wish to get involved. We can also integrate your non-financial assets, such as real estate, business interests, or art into our analysis.





Wealth management philosophy
You want your wealth to last. So do we. At Lombard Odier, it’s our guiding principle. And it has been for seven generations 
			Read more




Wealth services
We don’t simply focus on your financial portfolio. Our personalised approach is designed to help us understand your wider ambitions and objectives for your wealth. 
			Read more




Investment services
What are your investment objectives? We only recommend investments that are suitable for you, that we understand and would be prepared to invest in ourselves. 
			Read more




Acting responsibly
We take our social responsibilities seriously. As part of our firm’s own engagement, we’ve supported charities and the arts for over two centuries. 
			Read more




Transparent reporting
We believe in the strength of transparent reporting to give you more control. 
			Read more




Impact office
We can help you select investments that have a sustainable impact on the environment, society and the world. 
			Read more




Independent asset managers
Whether you are an independent asset manager or want to become one, we can help you to operate and develop your business to its full potential. 
			Read more









