PRIVATE CLIENTSAsset managementTECHNOLOGY & BANKING SERVICES



Asset management





Lombard Odier Investment Managers is the asset management business of Lombard Odier, focused on institutional investors, third-party distributors and financial intermediaries. Lombard Odier has always been wholly owned and managed by its partners who are responsible for the day-to-day management of the firm.
	This independent structure means that we are able to focus 100% on our clients rather than shareholders. And our size and focus means that we can respond with agility to market events.


Our 111 investment professionals have an average of 16 years industry experience. We have over 300 staff operating from 13 offices worldwide.

Our investment pillars
	Successfully exploiting the investment opportunities created by market dislocations requires skill and experience. We believe that to achieve this consistently over the long term also requires independent thinking and a specialist approach.  For us, this specialist approach involves focusing on those investment strategies where we believe that we can add real value for our clients.

	 





Fixed Income
We are in a new paradigm in fixed income markets presenting significant challenges for investors and asset owners. Our full range of fixed income strategies and solutions in developed markets, emerging markets and corporates have been designed to meet these challenges. 
			Read more




Convertibles
For investors allocating to the compelling benefits of convertible bonds, we are a natural choice. Lombard Odier Investment Managers is a market leader in convertible bonds with a comprehensive range of strategies and solutions managed by an experienced team. 
			Read more




Equities
Our high conviction approach is characterised by our dedicated investment teams’ desire to thoroughly research each company or issuer within the investment universe and to know the factors that influence their returns. Our high conviction equity capabilities span core regional strategies in emerging markets, Europe and Switzerland as well as global thematic strategies.  Our systematic equity capabilities apply an innovative factor-based approach offering diversified and well-balanced multi-factor exposure in key regional allocations such as US, Europe and Emerging Markets. 
			Read more




Multi-asset
We believe that focusing on investors’ outcomes and applying a risk-based asset allocation is key to achieving better diversification, capital protection and stable long-term performance.  In our view, clients’ objectives should be clearly defined in terms of desired outcomes and should be translated into a risk budget, rather than targeted returns. 
			Read more




Alternatives
Our Alternative investment teams target returns that are uncorrelated to market cycles and free from any systematic factors.  We also manage less liquid strategies which are designed to benefit from an illiquidity premium and aim to provide long-term protection from inflation. 
			Read more




Impact Investing
We are committed to preserving the long-term interests of our clients. This commitment also extends to our employees and the communities with which we operate.  As a pioneer in this field, we believe in the power of investment to bring about positive, social and environmental change is folded into our company history, as we strive to offer our clients financial and social returns without compromise. 
			Read more










