July 25, 2017 9:56 PM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of Lombard Odier Asset Management (USA) Corp



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Lombard Odier Asset Management (USA) Corp is a privately owned hedge fund manager. The firm primarily caters to pooled investment vehicles. It launches and manages equity, fixed income, and balanced mutual funds for its clients. The firm also manages hedge funds for its clients. It invests in the public equity, fixed income, and alternative investment markets. The firm employs multi-strategy approach to investing. It employs fundamental analysis with bottom-up stock picking approach to make its investments. The firm operates as a subsidiary of Lombard Odier Darier Hentsch & Cie Asset Management. Lombard Odier Asset Management (USA) Corp was founded in 2007 and is based in New York City with ...
Lombard Odier Asset Management (USA) Corp is a privately owned hedge fund manager. The firm primarily caters to pooled investment vehicles. It launches and manages equity, fixed income, and balanced mutual funds for its clients. The firm also manages hedge funds for its clients. It invests in the public equity, fixed income, and alternative investment markets. The firm employs multi-strategy approach to investing. It employs fundamental analysis with bottom-up stock picking approach to make its investments. The firm operates as a subsidiary of Lombard Odier Darier Hentsch & Cie Asset Management. Lombard Odier Asset Management (USA) Corp was founded in 2007 and is based in New York City with additional offices in Geneva, Switzerland and London, United Kingdom.
Detailed Description


